            Scalability: Expands easily with new devices and growing data.
            Data Management: Organizes and categorizes data for easy retrieval.
            Security: Uses encryption and access controls to protect data.
            Integration: Syncs with the Smart Home system for seamless operation. In essence, memory tapes act as a cloud-like storage system that securely manages and accesses data for smart home devices.</p>
